  "message": "Remove invalid config option from mdx.nvim plugin\n\nThe mdx.nvim plugin only provides treesitter filetype detection and has\nno setup() function. The `config = true` option caused lazy.nvim to look\nfor a nonexistent configuration module.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
